name: EUCALYPTUS STRAWBERRY GUM OIL
description: Eucalyptus Strawberry Gum Oil, commonly known as Strawberry gum is a fairly unusual essential oil, not commonly found on the commercial market. Eucalyptus olida was initially wild harvested, but plantations now supply the current industry demand. Technically a resin at room temperature rather than an oil, it contains over 98% methyl cinnamate.Methyl cinnamate, an aromatic ether, is found in a variety of fruits and herbs such as tarragon, Sichuan pepper, galangal and some species or varieties of basil.
